assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Tokuden Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells welding materials in Japan. The company offers flux-cored wires for submerged arc welding and MAG welding, arc welding electrodes for hard facing, wire rods for TIG and MIG welding, agglomerated and fused fluxes, powdered material for PTA welding, etc. It also undertakes welding construction works, such as various types of welding and overhaul works to iron-making, petrochemicals, cement, home electronics, automobile, and foodstuff industries; and provides top plates, pipes, iron foundry press-equalizing devices, trunnion journals, and chutes, as well as environment-related equipment, including deodorizing devices and forced-cooling apparatus. In addition, it is involved in the manufacture and sale of various welding equipment, and industrial machinery and equipment. Tokuden Co., Ltd. was founded in 1933 and is headquartered in Amagasaki, Japan.
